    <h2 class="sect-title">About Nolan Hill</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">A family-friendly neighborhood, the community in Nolan Hill combines the scenic beauty of Nature with modern-age conveniences and facilities.</p>
            <p class="par-xl">Homes for sale in Nolan Hill include a variety of architectural styles from single-family detached homes to condos and even palatial bungalows with sprawling yards to suit the needs of all kinds of homebuyers.</p>
